programme.desc: Hani masih merajuk dan Mizan masih memujuknya. Di pejabat, Dzul berbincang dengan Mizan tentang Shariff. Nizam yang berjumpa Hani tempuh hari juga berhasrat Hani terima tawaran temuduga kerja di Johor, lagi pun dia juga dapat kerja baru di Johor. Hani hanya menjawab soal itu dia perlu berbincang dengan Mizan. Dengan situasi begitu, Nizam bertekad akan perolehi juga Hani dan sekali lagi dia meminta Suraya melakukan porak peranda di rumah tangga Hani/Mizan. Sementara itu, Sheila juga bertekad agar Nizam tetap akan dicari dan didampinginya. Di pejabat, Mizan berkongsi dan menceritakan situasi dia dengan isterinya kepada Dzul antara yang terpenting Mizan memang mengharapkan satu ketika dia akan menceraikan isterinya secara baik. Selain itu, mengakui tidak pernah menyentuh isterinya pun. Mizan juga diarah untuk menguruskan satu projek syarikat di luar negara. Semasa Hani hadir temuduga, dia juga tidak menyangka orang yang akan menemuduga itu Shariff. Kebetulan Mizan datang berjumpa Shariff hendak bercakap hal pekerjaan, semasa dia memasuki ke bilik Shariff, Hani bersembunyi ditepi meja

programme.desc: Cerita berpusat pada Kirana (dilakonkan oleh Titi Kamal), seorang suri rumah yang dahulunya adalah pelajar popular dan cemerlang di sekolah. Namun, selepas berkahwin dengan Ben (Raffi Ahmad) dan mempunyai dua anak, Kirana mula merasa tidak yakin diri dan bosan dengan kehidupannya sebagai suri rumah. Suatu hari, Kirana menghadiri perjumpaan semula sekolah menengah dan bertemu dengan sahabat lamanya, Diana (Donita), yang berjaya dalam kerjayanya. Kirana kemudian mengunjungi gerai ramalan dan secara ajaib bertukar tempat dengan Diana, menjadi wanita kerjaya yang berjaya. Namun, Kirana segera menyedari bahawa kehidupan yang diimpikannya tidak seindah yang dibayangkan dan mula merindukan keluarganya.

programme.title: Suamiku Mr Blind S1 Ep29
programme.desc: Ain rasa terkejut dan bersalah dengan Aidil. Dia takut dosa dan derhakanya pada Aidil buatnya susah hendak bersalin. Jadi dia penuhi masa-masa akhir sebelum bersalin dengan berbaik dan solat berjemaah dengan Aidil. Dalam masa yang sama dia juga rasa bersalah kerana Aidil sanggup terima wanita yang pernah butakannya dulu dan menyayanginya sepenuh jiwa. Tetapi ada masa-masanya Ain teringat perbuatan Aidil padanya dan kembali marah. Sampai satu tahap, Aidil sudah tidak tahan dan keluar daripada rumah. Nak dijadikan cerita, air ketuban Ain pecah ketika itu dan cuba hubungi Aidil malangnya tidak berangkat.

Setelah keadaan Syed Redza kembali stabil, Syed Redza dibawa pulang semula ke rumah. Zureen meminta maaf di atas perbuatannya. Syed Redza mengambil kesempatan membuli Zureen. Zureen menerima segala perlakuan Syed Redza dengan tabah.

programme.title: Nasi Kerabu Untuk Che Abe Ep03
programme.desc: Ibu shira dapat rasakan Shira dilamun cinta kerana sanggup cuba makan budu. Cuti pertengahan semester bermula dan Faizul balik ke Kelantan. Setibanya di rumah dia terkejut Mek Yan Mek Yan marah Atikah teruk sebab difitnah orang kampung. Faizul meminta Mek Yan izinkan sahaja Atikah berkahwin dengan Mat Yie. Faizul dapat panggilan, teruja sangat apabila tahu Shira dekat Kota Bahru. Shira sanggup tipu semua orang konon ada urusan bisnes semata-mata mahu jumpa Faizul. Mereka seronok luangkan masa bersama dan perasaan mereka semakin mendalam. Faizul jemput shira ke rumahnya. Mek Yan bimbang Shira moden tak bertudung berbanding Pia, anak Tok Imam yang dia mahu jodohkan dengan Faizul.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep01
programme.desc: Ezgi, pada pesta ulang tahun mengejutnya untuk teman lelakinya Soner, mengetahui bahawa dia curang dengannya. Hari-hari sukar bermula lagi untuk Ezgi. Ezgi, yang terpaksa meninggalkan rumah di mana dia tinggal bersama Soner, juga kehilangan pekerjaannya. Proses ini menyebabkan mereka membuat keputusan baru. Untuk menjauhi lelaki "Salah" dan mencari lelaki yang betul. Orang yang akan membantunya melaksanakan keputusan ini ialah jiran baharunya, zgr, yang merupakan "cikgu yang salah" dalam setiap erti kata.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep02
programme.desc: Ezgi ingin berjumpa dengan Serdar sekali lagi untuk menebus kesilapannya. Dia meminta Cansu untuk mengatur pertemuan lain. Kali ini, dia bertekad untuk bertindak dengan betul dan mempengaruhi Serdar. Dia perlukan zgr untuk ini. Jadi dia menerima tawaran zgr. Mereka membuat perjanjian. Ezgi akan bertindak seperti teman wanita zgr untuk satu malam, dan sebagai balasan zgr akan mengajarnya apa yang perlu dilakukan untuk menarik perhatian Serdar. Walau bagaimanapun, perjanjian ini akan mempunyai keputusan yang berbeza untuk kedua-duanya.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep03
programme.desc: Ezgi dan zgr, yang kali terakhir bergaduh dan membatalkan perjanjian itu, terkejut apabila mereka mengetahui bahawa mereka akan bekerjasama. Ozan, yang menyaksikan detik-detik ini, tidak tahu apa yang perlu dilakukan. Adalah sangat penting bagi Ozan untuk bekerjasama dengan Ezgi, walaupun dia bercakap dengan zgr dan cuba membetulkan keadaan ia tidak berjaya. Sementara itu, kejutan kedua menanti Ezgi. Dalam menghadapi kejadian ini, Ezgi menyoal dirinya sendiri dan menganggap dia bertindak salah dengan zgr. Dia mahu membetulkan hubungannya dengan zgr. Keinginan Ezgi untuk datang ke majlis perkahwinan membuatkan zgr gembira. Kedua-duanya bersedia untuk bermain permainan, tidak menyedari apa yang akan berlaku kepada mereka.

programme.title: Bawah Payung Awan Ep09
programme.desc: Hanan mengaku yang dia dan Soleiman pernah terlanjur. Widad keliru sama ada dia masih mampu mempercayai Soleiman. Hanan menipu Widad untuk memenuhi permintaan Zaf yang ingin mengambil kesempatan ke atasnya.

programme.title: Bawah Payung Awan Ep10
programme.desc: Widad enggan mempercayai Hanan lagi selepas insiden lepas. Sewaktu sedang bekerja di restoren, Widad didatangi Zaf yang cuba membalas dendam. Raykal yang berada bersamanya terheret sekali ke dalam situasi tersebut.

programme.title: Bawah Payung Awan Ep11
programme.desc: Usaha Hanan untuk mendapatkan kepercayaan Widad semula gagal. Hanan yang terdesak mula mengugut Thaqif selepas mengetahui rahsia antara dia dan Basri. Anita cuba menghalang Widad dari terus berkawan dengan Soleiman.

programme.title: Bawah Payung Awan Ep12
programme.desc: Hanan memberitahu Basri dan Thaqif yang dia mengandung. Dia cuba mempengaruhi Soleiman untuk menyertai Basri supaya mereka beroleh wang untuk anak dalam kandungannya. Soleiman serba-salah kerana tak mahu Widad terlibat.

programme.title: Kesempatan Keduda
programme.desc: Cerita berpusat pada Abi (Raffi Ahmad), seorang pekerja korporat yang baru sahaja bercerai dengan isterinya, Maya (Dinda Kanya Dewi), kerana masalah perselingkuhan. Di sisi lain, Ken (Zizan Razak) juga mengalami perceraian dengan isterinya, Baby (Nagita Slavina). Selepas persidangan perceraian, Abi dan Ken bertemu di sebuah warung kopi dan mula berkongsi cerita tentang kehidupan mereka. Mereka berdua merasa bahawa perceraian adalah titik terendah dalam hidup mereka, tetapi pemilik warung kopi memberi mereka perspektif baru bahawa menjadi duda bukanlah akhir segalanya. Abi dan Ken kemudian memutuskan untuk move on dari masa lalu mereka dan memulakan petualangan baru dalam mencari pasangan hidup. Mereka berkenalan dengan dua wanita cantik, Syafa (Cut Meyriska) dan Dianti (Marsha Aruan), tetapi menghadapi pelbagai rintangan, termasuk kehadiran mantan kekasih Syafa, Diego (Bastian Steel)

Sementara itu, Val memberi bayangan kepada pereka tempatan yang berpengaruh dan Sheila menetapkan malam K-drama sebagai acara mingguan biasa.

programme.title: K-Love Ep06
programme.desc: Jay memutuskan antara protokol dan hati nuraninya apabila lebih banyak isu di ladang timbul. Val cuba menghalang pembekalnya daripada tarik diri dan mempertahankan syarikat daripada khabar angin berniat jahat, manakala Tish cuba mendapatkan klien walaupun klien itu ragu-ragu terhadap dia dan syarikatnya. Sheila membentangkan rancangannya untuk perjumpaan besar itu.

programme.title: Sampai 7 Keturunan
programme.desc: Dalam sebuah peraduan, Aidil memenangi percutian lima bintang dan wang tunai, tetapi memilih untuk tidak menggunakannya kerana isterinya sarat mengandung. Dia menyerahkan hadiah itu kepada Pak Karim, yang enggan pergi kerana risaukan ayam kesayangannya. Setelah dipujuk, Pak Karim akhirnya menerima tawaran, tetapi kehadiran ayamnya menyebabkan ketidakselesaan di hotel dan berita tentang virus H5N1 mula tersebar, merosakkan reputasi hotel. Dalam perjalanan itu, Pak Karim bertemu dengan Shida, bekas isterinya, dan mereka berdua mula merasakan kembali cinta lama. Ketika cuti hampir tamat, Pak Karim merancang untuk pulang, tetapi Shida menyatakan hasrat untuk bersatu semula, menyebabkan Aidil dan isterinya yang sebenarnya merancang pertemuan ini turut hadir melihat ibu bapa mereka kembali bersama.

programme.title: Senario Lang Buana
programme.desc: Filem ini membawa penonton ke era zaman lampau iaitu sebelum abad ke-19 tetapi kisah yang dipaparkan berkaitan dengan masyarakat Malaysia hari ini. Ia mengisahkan tiga orang pemuda - Gunung, Daik dan Bercabang - yang melarikan diri daripada menjadi hamba abdi kepada Orang Kaya Seri Bentan. Mereka bertiga berhenti di sebuah kota bernama Lang Buana di pinggir sebuah sungai. Setibanya di kota itu, mereka disambut meriah kerana disangka putera raja yang dapat menyelamatkan kota itu daripada serangan Sang Nira. Terperangkap oleh keadaan, ketiga-tiga pemuda berkenaan terpaksa menyamar menjadi putera raja dan merangka taktik peperangan bagi memperkuatkan benteng pertahanan Lang Buana.

programme.title: Dapur Panas S10 Ep10

programme.title: Anggun Mikayla Ep10
programme.desc: Perjalanan hidup Mikayla sentiasa bersimpang-siur dengan dugaan sejak dia mencelikkan mata birunya ke dunia. Status kelahirannya membuatkan dia seringkali menerima cacian penduduk kampung dan menjadi mangsa buli semasa kecil. Mekap adalah cara Mikayla menidakkan kewujudannya sendiri. Dia berselindung di sebalik rambut palsu hitam untuk menyorokkan rambut auburnnya serta mengenakan pelbagai jenis mekap untuk menggelapkan warna kulit kerana keinginannya untuk tampak Melayu. Siang, Mikayla bekerja sebagai jurumekap artis dan apabila malam tiba, dia menjelma sebagai pontianak. Pertemuan Mikayla dengan Idriz dalam satu insiden lucu telah mencipta satu hubungan aneh yang tidak bernama. Dalam diam, Idriz menyimpan rasa tetapi keinginannya terbatas kerana tanggungjawabnya pada keluarga. Jurugambar yang bekerja bersamanya, Asif yang suka mengusik Mikayla mulai tersedar yang usikannya sudah bertukar menjadi perasaan sebenar. Tetapi, dia terlajak memikat pelakon popular bernama Andria, sebelum tersedar tentang perasaannya terhadap Mikayla. Sedang Mikayla dalam keadaan celaru, lelaki dari masa silamnya, Aidan pula muncul kembali, menagih kemaafan kerana meninggalkan parut panjang di dahinya. Aidan yang kini sudah bergelar pelakon popular cuba memadamkan kenangan sakit mereka demi merebut hati yang dirinduinya itu. Tetapi, impian Mikayla hanya satu, berhadapan dengan masa silamnya dan mencantas kebencian mama. Cinta bukan destinasi yang diimpi. Namun, hatinya terus menjadi buruan oleh tiga orang lelaki.

Alina terpaksa berhenti sekolah walaupun mendapat kelulusan cemerlang dalam peperiksaan SPM. Beliau terpaksa bekerja mencuci dan membersih rumah penduduk, termasuk rumah Nek Timah dan Imah bagi menampung keperluan keluarga. Alina tidak mahu Alisa berhenti sekolah sepertinya. Alisa pelajar cemerlang, sedang bersaing dengan Mei Fen menjadi pelajar cemerlang bagi mendapat hadiah RM20 ribu. Satu hari, Lina pergi menjenguk Nek TImah dan bertembung dengan kekasih lamanya, Shazman anak kepada Imah yang kini berjaya menghabiskan pelajaran di kolej. Lina ditegur Nad, kawan lama sekolah Lina dan juga cucu kepada Nek Timah ketika berada di rumah Nek Timah. Lina terpaku dengan kecantikan dan kekayaan Nad. Lina ternampak mesej dari Mika di telefon Nad dan mula ragu-ragu dengan pekerjaannya. Nad pula mulai berbaik dengan Lisa kerana dia mempunyai agenda tersendiri bagi memerangkap Lisa bekerja sepertinya sebagai Sugar Baby.

programme.title: The Gadis Ep02
programme.desc: Nad mendapat mesej dari Mika menuntut hutangnya dibayar. Dia sedang menjaga Nek Timah di rumah. Ibu Shazman datang melawat Nek Timah dan berkenan dengan kecantikan Nad yang cantik dan berjaya. Bercadang menjodohkan Nad dengan Shazman, yang juga seorang graduan kolej, bagaimanapun menjadi marah selepas diberitahu Nek Timah Shazman sukakan Lina. Sementara itu Lisa dan Rocky masih tidak puas hati dengan kepandaian Mei Fen. Ketika Lisa dia sedang berjalan balik dari sekolah, Nad lalu dan mengajaknya keluar makan. Di Restoran, Mika masih menelefon Nad untuk mencari seseorang yang baru untuk menyertai kerja mereka sebagai sugar baby. Nad mendapat idea apabila melihat Lisa bagi memerangkap gadis tersebut. Ibu Shazman dengan sengaja menyuruh Lina ke rumahnya dan menyuruh dia menjadi orang gaji. Shazman merasa bersalah melihat keadaan Lina.

Ketika cuti hampir tamat, Pak Karim merancang untuk pulang, tetapi Shida menyatakan hasrat untuk bersatu semula, menyebabkan Aidil dan isterinya yang sebenarnya merancang pertemuan ini turut hadir melihat ibu bapa mereka kembali bersama.

programme.desc: Rock Bro! diceritakan melalui naratif Jijoe, kemuncak pencapaian mereka apabila menjadi finalis Anugerah Juara Lagu, namun era rock mula meniti fasa kejatuhan dengan kemasukan aliran muzik rap dan hip-hop pada awal 90-an. Amy Mat Piah meninggalkan jawatan sebagai pengurus kumpulan Rimba Bara kerana keinginanya yang terlalu kuat untuk menjadi penyanyi Rock. Namun begitu,o kumpulan Rimba Bara tetap meneruskan perjuangan musik mereka..Rimba Bara menerima seorang pembantu bernama Dio. programme.title: Spirits War
programme.desc: Petualangan berlangsung di tanah perbatasan Siam yang penuh kedamaian dan kebahagiaan, hingga Tuan Panwa memutuskan untuk menambang gunung di Dekat Hutan Kegelapan. Sedikit yang Tuan Panwa tahu bahwa gunung tersebut adalah situs sebuah tanah pemakaman kuno.

programme.title: Ghost Writer 2
programme.desc: Kejayaan novel keduanya mengharumkan nama Naya. Malangnya dia lebih dilabelkan sebagai psikik daripada penulis. Ini membuatkan Naya geram dan berat hati untuk berhadapan dengan dunia berhantu itu semula. Namun, segalanya berubah apabila bakal suaminya Vino meninggal dunia secara tiba-tiba.

programme.title: Samson
programme.desc: Selepas kehilangan cinta dalam hidupnya kepada seorang Putera Filistin yang kejam, seorang pemuda Ibrani dengan kekuatan ghaib membela rakyatnya, mengorbankan segala-galanya untuk membalas cintanya, umatnya, dan Tuhan.

programme.title: Jangan Ikut Aku Ep 11 Ep11
programme.desc: Akil tidak lagi tahan dengan cerita orang-orang mengenai saka-saka yang berkeliaran di taman perumahan tempat Akil tinggal. Sebab itu jugalah dia bertengkar dengan kawan baiknya,Nabil. Akil panggil semua saka-saka dan memberi amaran supaya mereka pergi. Saka-saka itu enggan dan Akil cuba mendapat pertolongan pawang untuk menghalau saka-saka tersebut. Sedang pawang bermentera menghalau saka-saka itu, Sahak berlari menemui Pak Sudin di surau dan beritahu yang dia ternampak saka dekat rumahnya dan hantu-hantu itu dibela oleh Akil. Sahak sangat marahkan Akil. Cikgu Shila juga marahkan Akil dan semasa menemui Pak Sudin, Akil diberi nasihat supaya segera melepaskan saka-saka itu sebelum apa-apa perkara buruk berlaku. Akil memberi amaran supaya saka-saka-itu pergi dan kalau gagal, tahulah apa yang hendak di lakukannya.

programme.title: Barajiwa Ep 6 Ep6
programme.desc: Noramina kagum dengan kemahiran bertarung Uzair dan menawar pekerjaan sebagai pengawal peribadinya. Uzair kini mempunyai pekerjaan yang sesuai dan boleh menyewa tempat tinggal sendiri. Hatta mula sedar ada sesuatu yang baik dan istimewa pada Uzair. Uzair mula mesra dengan Noramina.

programme.title: Budak Magik Ep 3 Ep3
programme.desc: Imran, Maira, Haikal dan Zara dikejutkan dengan kejadian aneh sebaik pulih dari demam. Mereka seakan-akan memiliki tenaga dan kuasa luar biasa yang mungkin ada kaitan dengan lintasan cahaya yang mereka lihat tempoh hari. Haikal memiliki kelebihan berlari sepantas kilat sementara Zara pula memiliki kuasa jeritan yang mampu memusnahkan. Juga dipaparkan kisah Imran menjejaki bola cahaya yang telah membawanya ke satu kawasan hutan sehingga dia hilang panduan untuk keluar

programme.title: Taxi 4
programme.desc: Tidak bernasib baik, kikir, tetapi menawan, detektif PD Marseille milien Coutant-Kerbalec mesti membantu komisioner Gibert yang lebih teruk daripada Clouseau menjaga penjenayah Belgium yang terkenal sebagai bahaya sama seperti - dan ditawan seperti Hannibal Lector. Kawan sejuk milien, pemandu teksi Daniel Morales, pada mulanya hanya bersetuju untuk menjaga anak-anak lelaki kawan mereka, kerana isteri milien, Petra, sedang menjalankan misi rahsia. Tetapi tidak lama kemudian, penjenayah Belgium itu melarikan diri, dan semasa mengejarnya, rakan-rakan itu tersandung pada satu perampokan bank dan sebuah vila megah milik raja dadah, di mana babak akhir yang hebat berlaku.

programme.title: Binhi
programme.desc: Daniel dan Cynthia, pasangan muda dengan anak dalam perjalanan, mengalami masa sukar di Manila. Mereka kembali ke Baguio, tempat asal Daniel, untuk memulakan semula. Melalui kebaikan Alex, kawan Daniel zaman kanak-kanak yang kaya, mereka dapat tinggal di sebuah rumah besar, tanpa sewa; dan dia mendapat tawaran kerja juga. Segala-galanya seolah-olah jatuh pada tempatnya untuk mereka - atau begitulah yang mereka fikirkan - sehingga perkara aneh mula berlaku di rumah mereka.

programme.title: Vengeance Of An Assassin
programme.desc: The Assassins' Code - Berpegang teguh pada misi. Jangan sekali-kali mengalihkan pandangan anda dari sasaran. Tidak menunjukkan belas kasihan. Natee (Dan Chupong) menjadi pembunuh kerana satu sebab- untuk mengetahui siapa yang membunuh ibu bapanya. Apabila dia semakin hampir untuk mendedahkan rangkaian rahsia kuasa dan rasuah, dia melakukan dua kali ganda dalam kerja, menjadikannya sasaran dan meletakkan semua orang yang dia sayangi dalam bahaya. Dikhianati, didedahkan dan diburu oleh pembunuh paling maut dalam perniagaan, kini Natee mempunyai kod baharu. Jadi lebih pantas. Lebih kuat. Pukul lebih kuat. Bertahan.

programme.title: On Halloween
programme.desc: Satu siri kematian dan kehilangan kejam membawa kembali kepada legenda bandar tentang badut pembunuh bersiri. Sekumpulan pelajar kolej akan menghadapi mimpi ngeri terburuk mereka, apabila Badut jahat ini kembali dari masa lalu pada Halloween.

programme.title: Interchange
programme.desc: Dihantui oleh penglihatan yang suram, jurugambar forensik Adam berundur dari dunia, tinggal di rumah dan mengambil gambar jirannya sehingga dia diseret ke dalam penyiasatan lain oleh kawan baiknya, Detektif Man, yang meminta bantuannya untuk menyelesaikan siri pembunuhan ritual yang mengerikan. Pada masa yang sama, hobi Adam yang kelihatan tidak berbahaya tidak lama kemudian menjadi lebih gelap apabila dia mengintip Iva, seorang wanita muda dari Borneo. Terpesona olehnya, dia tidak lama lagi terjerat dalam rangkaian misteri dan pembunuhannya. Ketika Adam diseret lebih jauh ke dalam dunia puak Iva dan Man menyelidiki penyiasatannya dengan lebih mendalam, mereka menemui mistik bawah tanah bomoh dan makhluk ghaib di bandar itu.

programme.title: Araf 3
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang seorang wanita muda yang berjuang untuk menyelamatkan abangnya yang ditangkap oleh syaitan. Pada usia lapan tahun, Arda ditangkap oleh penyembah syaitan yang kuat. Kakak Arda, Nihal, melakukan yang terbaik untuk menyelamatkan abangnya daripada masalah ini, tetapi dia tidak dapat mencapai apa-apa keputusan. Nhal, yang mencuba segala cara untuk mencari penyelesaian, membawa abangnya ke doktor dan guru cinci, tetapi tiada apa yang berubah. Sementara itu, wanita muda itu mengetahui bahawa terdapat sebuah buku bernama Kitab'l Azazil, yang mengandungi mantera yang sangat kuat. Nihal yang merampas buku yang mengandungi jampi berbahaya dan maut untuk menyelamatkan abangnya, meminta kekasih dan dua rakan karibnya membantunya membuat jampi yang ditulis di sini. Empat orang muda berkumpul di sebuah rumah dan berjaya menyelamatkan Arda dengan sihir yang mereka lemparkan. Walau bagaimanapun, dengan sihir yang mereka lemparkan, pemuda itu menyebabkan syaitan paling kuat yang pernah dilihat dibebaskan.

programme.title: Ong Bak 2
programme.desc: Berlatarkan Thailand abad ke-15, filem ini berkisarkan Tien, anak kepada seorang bangsawan yang dibunuh. Ditawan dan dijual sebagai hamba, Tien diselamatkan daripada kematian oleh Chernang, ketua Pha Beek Khrut, sekumpulan artis mempertahankan diri yang pakar dalam pelbagai gaya tempur Asia.

programme.title: Gangster
programme.desc: Berdasarkan geng-geng Bangkok yang terkenal pada tahun 1950-an-60an. Kisah ini mengikuti seorang banduan yang baru dibebaskan yang ingin hidup lurus, tetapi tidak mengetahui apa-apa selain kehidupan seorang samseng, dia kembali kepada kumpulan lamanya.

programme.title: 3AM Ep 4 Ep4
programme.desc: Pesta Hantu Lapar sudah hampir. Seorang pekerja baru di telah menyinggung perasaan hantu di bangunan pejabatnya kerana dia tidak hormat kepada roh pada hari pertamanya bekerja. Semasa menjalani syif malam, lelaki itu dan rakan sekerjanya yang bekerja lebih masa mengalami pertemuan menyeramkan yang membuatkan mereka merenung tingkah laku dan kepercayaan mereka.

programme.title: Barajiwa Ep 7 Ep7
programme.desc: Ashikin dan Uzair kembali bersama tetapi Imran sedaya upaya mendapatkan Ashikin kembali. Rakan-rakan Uzair datang menyokong Uzair dan Ashikin. Uzair terkejut apabila Hatta datang berlawan dengannya menentang Imran. Mereka cuba melarikan diri dari bandar tetapi Imran menggunakan Ajeeb mempunyai umpan.

programme.title: Santau Merasuk Ep 8 Ep8
programme.desc: HALIM bersama NINA mengambil MAT di hospital. NINA perasan dirinya diekori satu sosok lembaga. ARIFAH yang sedang membuat persiapan jamuan kepulangan MAT didatangi FAREL dan ECHA yang menghantar makanan. Kemudian disusuli oleh HUSIN yang turut menghantar makanan.MAT yang menyedari isterinya sudah terkena sihir cuba menngubati tetapi gagal. ARIFAH tetap menafikan setiap tekaan MAT demi mengelak MAYA terus berdendam. ARIFAH meninggal dunia akibat serangan penyakit misteri. MAT tidak dapat menerima kematian ARIFAHd an terus membawa diri dari situ. Dendam di hati seolah masih tidak terlerai.

programme.title: The Secret Of Sinchanee
programme.desc: Seorang pemandu trak tunda industri yang mengalami insomnia kembali ke rumah zaman kanak-kanaknya selepas kematian bapanya, untuk mengetahui bahawa kehadiran paranormal telah tinggal di rumah itu dan menghantui tanah suci yang dibina di atasnya.

Duo ini akan bekerjasama dengan ahli paranormal tempatan yang lain untuk mendapat akses ke tempat-tempat berhantu dan luar biasa di Malaysia.

programme.title: Siccin 5
programme.desc: Hale menarik perhatian dengan penampilannya yang berbeza dan tingkah laku yang pelik. Dia tinggal di rumah bersejarah dan menakutkan di Nevsehir bersama ibunya, seorang nenek yang tertekan dan ibu saudaranya Azra. Bapa Hale telah hilang sebelum dia dilahirkan dan tidak pernah dilihat lagi. Hale melihat mimpi ngeri malam yang dahsyat; bapanya, yang tidak pernah dilihatnya, menjemputnya ke sebuah rumah tua dan luar biasa.

programme.title: Janin Tak Berdosa
programme.desc: Pasangan suami isteri muda Firman dan Julia merancang berbulan madu di Amsterdam selepas Firman mendapat kenaikan pangkat di syarikatnya. Oleh kerana pada masa itu Julia mengandung dan beliau ingin meneruskan percutiannya maka mereka merancang menggugurkan kandungan itu.

programme.title: Galaxy Games
programme.desc: Sekumpulan orang dewasa muda dihantar ke planet yang jauh untuk bersaing dalam permainan Sol Invictus yang berprestij.

programme.title: The Secret Suster Ngesot Urban
programme.desc: Mengetahui bahawa bapanya telah berkahwin dengan seorang wanita sebayanya, Kanaya meninggalkan rumah, hanya untuk mengalami kemalangan yang menyebabkan dia di hospital berhantu.

programme.title: The Night Sitter
programme.desc: Seorang penipu menyamar sebagai pengasuh kanak-kanak untuk merompak rumah seorang ahli ghaib yang kaya dan anak lelakinya yang masih kecil. Tetapi apabila rakan sejenayahnya tiba, budak lelaki itu memanggil trio ahli sihir yang melayan penjahat itu ke malam kekacauan.

programme.title: Algojo: Perang Santet
programme.desc: Desta dilahirkan dalam keluarga bahagia. Namun, kebahagiaan dalam keluarga tidak kekal lama apabila hantaran sihir membawa kepada kematian kedua ibu bapa. Desta membesar menjadi seorang yang menyendiri dan penuh misteri. Keinginannya untuk membalas dendam membuatkan dia mencari dalang di sebalik kematian ibu bapanya.

programme.title: Den Budak Motor
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang Deniel, seorang lelaki yang kecewa ditinggalkan oleh bekas kekasihnya, Sarah disebabkan kesusahan Deniel yang hanya memiliki motor kapcai.

programme.title: Barajiwa Ep 7 Ep7
programme.desc: Ashikin dan Uzair kembali bersama tetapi Imran sedaya upaya mendapatkan Ashikin kembali. Rakan-rakan Uzair datang menyokong Uzair dan Ashikin. Uzair terkejut apabila Hatta datang berlawan dengannya menentang Imran. Mereka cuba melarikan diri dari bandar tetapi Imran menggunakan Ajeeb mempunyai umpan.

programme.title: Barajiwa Ep 1 Ep1
programme.desc: Uzair dan Madi adalah musuh sekolah. Apabila Madi menghina kawannya Suresh, Uzair menyerang Madi. Madi membalas dengan menyerang rakan-rakan Uzair. Pidottrauma dengan serangan Madi tetapi Uzair cuba untuk menenangkan keadaan. Namun, apabila Madi menyedari bahawa CIkgu Sofi mempunyai sifatlemah lembut terhadap Uzair, Madi menyerang dan menyakiti Cikgu Sofi.

programme.title: Barajiwa Ep 2 Ep2
programme.desc: Uzair menyerang Madi dengan ganas. Madi dimasukkan ke hospital dalam keadaan koma, Uzair dihantar untuk pemulihan. Uzair menumpukan perhatian kepada SPM. Dia pergi untuk melindungi Ajeeb daripada Hatta yang membawa kepada lebih banyak pergaduhan. Imran membalas dendam terhadap Uzair dengan memanipulasi Asyikin untuk menjadi GRO.

programme.title: Barajiwa Ep 3 Ep3
programme.desc: Apabila Uzair pulang ke rumah untuk bersama adik dan ibunya, dia dihalau oleh ibunya yang tidak mahu dia tinggal bersama mereka. Uzair mendapattahu bahawa Ashikin telah disimpan oleh Imran dan dia pergi untuk menyelamatkannya. Apabila Ashikin menyuruh melupakannya, Uzair kecewa dan pergi ke bandar.

programme.title: Barajiwa Ep 4 Ep4
programme.desc: Abang Man memperkenalkan Uzair tentang kehidupan di KL dengan mengajarnya tentang perlawanan di gelanggang haram dan mendapatkan Uzair pekerjaan di tempat cuci kereta. Di KL, Uzair bertemu semula dengan Ajeeb yang kini menjadi busker jalanan dan tinggal di bawah jambatan. Hatta datang untuk melawan Uzair di gelanggang haram untuk menyelesaikan hutang lama.

programme.title: You Saka.. Pergi Jauh Jauh Ep 1 Ep1
programme.desc: Episod Pertama cereka komedi seram disusuli dengan kepercayaan khurafat ini berkisar kepada personaliti Nia. Nia sebagai setiausaha syarikat milik seorang Datin Salina yang amat menyukainya hingga bercadang untuk dijodohkan kepada anak lelakinya. Ibu Nia dikampung, sedang sakit dijagai oleh Roslan, bapa saudaranya (Pak Lang). Nia mempercayai dia wajar menyeru puteri yang sesekali Nia akan lakukan bertujuan melindunginya dan juga sebagai amalan turun temurunnya selama ini. Jika tidak dilakukan, saka berbentuk syaitan akan menggangguinya. Ada sebab-sebab bahawa ibunya memiliki saka dan kematiannya bererti saka itu cuba mempengaruhi warisnya iaitu Nia. Nia tinggal dengan Shasa dan sepupu Shasa iaitu, Adrus adalah 'boy friend' Nia. Adrus sedang menceburi kerjaya dalam bidang paranormal, merupakan anak Ibrahim seorang bomoh. Ketika ibu Nia meninggal dunia dia belum ketahui. Sementara itu, semasa pengembumian ibunya berlaku juga kekecuhan iaitu muncul lembaga putih (berbentuk manusia - wanita). Selain dari itu, sesekali saka Gelam berbentuk syaitan (hitam jalur hijau) mengganggui Nia, 'boy friend'nya dan pernah bersama lembaga putih mengganggui bomoh Ibrahim.

programme.title: Big Match
programme.desc: Choi Ik-Ho ialah bintang seni mempertahankan diri yang mempunyai bakat dalam aksi dan jenaka. Tetapi suatu hari, dia dijebak kerana membunuh. Ace ialah perancang permainan, yang membuat permainan untuk kelas atasan Korea. Dia adalah penjahat yang menjadikan bandar menjadi papan permainan besar melalui teknologi. Ace dan Choi Ik-Ho menjadi musuh apabila Choi Ik-Ho melompat ke dalam permainan untuk menyelamatkan adiknya.

programme.title: Yang Berhormat
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Kuping, anak gelandangan yang menjalani kehidupan di Kuala Lumpur dengan melakukan pelbagai pekerjaan. Dia bersahabat dengan seorang OKU bernama Lobak dan Mat Yee. Pada suatu hari, Kuping terserempak dengan seorang lelaki bernama YB Salleh Ali dan terpesona melihat beliau memberi ceramah politik. Kuping yang terinspirasi dengan YB Salleh Ali itu ingin membantu Lobak untuk memikat seorang gadis bernama Mastura.

programme.title: Setinggan
programme.desc: Kawasan setinggan yang dibangunkan di tapak kubur tali barut Jepun menimbulkan kekacauan terhadap penduduk di situ. Hantu-hantu kubur tersebut merayau dan menganggu ketenteraman penduduk di situ.

programme.title: Ekspresi
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang kanak-kanak bernama Awi yang kurang mendapat kasih sayang daripada ibu bapanya yang sibuk bekerja. Awi sering bergaul dengan budak-budak nakal di sekitar rumahnya. Keadaan menjadi semakin keruh setelah Awi mengetahui bahawa dia merupakan anak angkat dan bakal mendapat adik baru. Hal ini telah membuatkan Awi semakin memberontak sehingga dia cuba untuk membunuh ahli keluarganya.

programme.title: Imigran
programme.desc: Faridah, pekerja warga asing terlibat dalam kes jenayah apabila telah menjadi saksi kes pembunuhan. Bertemu Hisham ketika cuba melarikan diri, mereka berdua mula jatuh cinta selepas menghabiskan masa bersama di kampung Hisham. Konflik berlaku apabila penjenayah tersilap menculik orang yang menyebabkan Faridah dan Hisham perlu melakukan sesuatu untuk menyelamatkan Azura.

programme.title: Anak Bapak
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Hisyam yang menjaga bapanya yang mengalami masalah sering lupa. Pada suatu hari, Hisyam berang kerana bapanya telah membuat sesuatu yang menyebabkan huru hara di pejabatnya. Bapanya sedih dengan kejadian itu dan berjanji tidak akan mengulanginya. Kemudian, Hisyam menghidapi sejenis penyakit yang boleh membawa maut dan membuatkan bapanya pula mengambil alih tugas untuk menjaga Hisyam.

programme.title: Estet
programme.desc: Mengisahkan para pekerja estet Cinta Manis yang bakal bertarung dengan kumpulan estet Red Cobra dalam satu perlawanan bola sepak yang sudah 20 tahun tidak diadakan. Farid dan Shashi, dua pekerja estet yang berkawan sejak kecil, menjadi harapan pekerja estet yang lain untuk menyelamatkan penindasan yang dilakukan oleh kerani estet, Pooniah. Seorang gadis cantik bernama Geetha tertarik hati dengan Farid dan Shashi. Sesi latihan dikendalikan oleh Subramaniam iaitu bapa Geetha yang dilantik sebagai jurulatih. Ayah kepada Shashi, Apaa, adalah pemain bola yang sangat mahir, tetapi telah berlaku insiden semasa perlawanan bola sepak estet itu dahulu yang mana kakinya patah diterjah oleh Junna, seorang samseng estet yang sengaja ingin menamatkan karier Apaa atas upahan Pooniah 20 tahun yang lalu. Berjayakah Farid dan Shashi serta kawan-kawannya membebaskan pekerja estet Cinta Manis daripada penindasan Pooniah?

programme.title: Rentak Desa
programme.desc: Pencemaran alam menyebabkan penduduk kampung mula menunjuk perasaan. Mat Desa dan Wairah seringkali berasa bahawa penduduk di situ hanya hidup atas empati pemaju. Hanya kerana ingin membuat jalan raya, bukit dan pokok ditebang manakala sungai dicemari sisa bahan toksik - menyebabkan ikan mati dan beracun. Sebuah penemuan merungkai segalanya.

programme.title: Siapa Tak Sayang Bini 2
programme.desc: Merupakan lanjutan daripada kisah dua keluarga yang ingin mengawal pasangan masing-masing. Kisah kali ini bermula apabila Saiful ternampak Karim yang sudah tidak takut isteri berjalan dengan seorang wanita muda bernama Sephia. Karim sering mendengar luahan Sephia yang sedang bergaduh dengan teman lelakinya. Saiful yang suka menyibuk itu memberitahu perkara tersebut kepada Kasmah, isteri Karim. Pelbagai kekalutan berlaku setelah Kasmah mengesyaki suaminya berlaku curang dan meminta bantuan Kamisah untuk menyiasat perkara ini. Dalam masa yang sama, Karim dengan bantuan Kassim mencari jalan untuk menjernihkan keadaan.

programme.title: Siapa Tak Sayang Bini 2
programme.desc: Merupakan lanjutan daripada kisah dua keluarga yang ingin mengawal pasangan masing-masing. Kisah kali ini bermula apabila Saiful ternampak Karim yang sudah tidak takut isteri berjalan dengan seorang wanita muda bernama Sephia. Karim sering mendengar luahan Sephia yang sedang bergaduh dengan teman lelakinya. Saiful yang suka menyibuk itu memberitahu perkara tersebut kepada Kasmah, isteri Karim. Pelbagai kekalutan berlaku setelah Kasmah mengesyaki suaminya berlaku curang dan meminta bantuan Kamisah untuk menyiasat perkara ini. Dalam masa yang sama, Karim dengan bantuan Kassim mencari jalan untuk menjernihkan keadaan.

programme.title: Estet
programme.desc: Mengisahkan para pekerja estet Cinta Manis yang bakal bertarung dengan kumpulan estet Red Cobra dalam satu perlawanan bola sepak yang sudah 20 tahun tidak diadakan. Farid dan Shashi, dua pekerja estet yang berkawan sejak kecil, menjadi harapan pekerja estet yang lain untuk menyelamatkan penindasan yang dilakukan oleh kerani estet, Pooniah. Seorang gadis cantik bernama Geetha tertarik hati dengan Farid dan Shashi. Sesi latihan dikendalikan oleh Subramaniam iaitu bapa Geetha yang dilantik sebagai jurulatih. Ayah kepada Shashi, Apaa, adalah pemain bola yang sangat mahir, tetapi telah berlaku insiden semasa perlawanan bola sepak estet itu dahulu yang mana kakinya patah diterjah oleh Junna, seorang samseng estet yang sengaja ingin menamatkan karier Apaa atas upahan Pooniah 20 tahun yang lalu. Berjayakah Farid dan Shashi serta kawan-kawannya membebaskan pekerja estet Cinta Manis daripada penindasan Pooniah?

You-Tsai abandoned the family many years ago, leaving his wife Siou-Ying to shoulder the huge responsibility of the Jin family business selling fish products at market. Although Siou-Ying was betrayed by You-Tsai, she has still been a dutiful daughter to her mother-in-law, and has single-mindedly raised four children.

With 35 different routes, the show explores the citys hidden gems, local culture, and unique experiences. From bustling night markets to serene temples, Walker Fun Kaohsiung showcases the best of Kaohsiung.

programme.title: Have A Nice Dream (M) Ep26
programme.desc: Five young professionals with different life skills, team up for two days and one night trip, leading the audiance to explore the good life of nature and the beauty of the land of Taiwan.

This show offers a rich blend of fun and learning, ensuring every moment is both enjoyable and enlightening.

programme.title: Top Singers (T) Ep637
programme.desc: The show 'Top Singers' aims to spotlight outstanding Taiwanese singers and composers, setting a new standard in the industry. Combining elements of competition, variety, and personal stories, the show welcomes participants of all ages. Its goals include discovering grassroots talent, innovating Taiwanese song performance styles, and involving more local talent in song composition to infuse new life into Taiwanese music.

programme.desc: Every second counts in "Show Biz" to bring you with the most High Speed star news, exciting live shows and performers interviews.

programme.desc: Feng-Yi Li handles everything in the house while her husband, Shu-An, lounges and daydreams. She constantly worries about the love lives of their four daughters. Yi-Wan starts a relationship with a gang leaders son despite claiming to have never dated. Qing-Qing may be having an affair with a married man. Xiao-Xi is infatuated with the school team captain but is unaware of "the others." An-Qing returns from the US with her son after a failed marriage. When Feng-Yi suddenly disappears, the sisters realize they've neglected their mother, who has always supported them. Now they must find her and get their lives back on track.

programme.title: Show Biz (M) Ep970971
programme.desc: Every second counts in "Show Biz" to bring you with the most High Speed star news, exciting live shows and performers interviews.

programme.title: The Borderless World (M) Ep739
programme.desc: Journalist with an infallible nose for a story is leading the audience to explore the world. Exploring how people from different cultures overcome the challenges with collective wisdom.

programme.title: Mr.Player (M) Ep514
programme.desc: Depending on the locations of the missions, Jacky Wu, the leader of the home team, invites various celebrities to take on challenges and bring you excitement every week.

programme.title: A Hint of You (M) Ep6667
programme.desc: As the chef and owner of "All One Hundred" stir-fry restaurant, Ching-Yo Xia is determined to recreate the delicious fried rice her father used to make. To achieve this, she hones her culinary skills by learning from Master Chef Zhai-Yu Fu of a high-end teppanyaki restaurant. Despite her resilience and fearlessness in the face of challenges, Ching-Yo somehow manages to turn Culinary Prince Zhai-Yu's graceful life upside down!

programme.title: Leio
programme.desc: An ex-singer Kao returns to his hometown for a funeral and takes part in a water drilling contest to save his drought-stricken hometown, as well as to win a million dollar cash prize. However, what Kao and other contestants do not realize is that there is a fierce and deadly beast lurking underground who wants to eat them all!

programme.title: Young and Dangerous: Reloaded
programme.desc: In this remake of Young and Dangerous, Chan Ho Nam and his three buddies of the Hung Hing triad gang strive to fight for their own justice, further expanding their power in the triad and becoming a new legend...

programme.title: Sex and the Beauties
programme.desc: It is said that Hong Kong is a sexy and sexual city where life is breathtakingly fast but glamorous. Fear of marriage, single & successful psychiatrist, Selina and other beauties seek for love and happy endings.

programme.title: Deception of the Novelist
programme.desc: This is a sexy thriller adapted from the hit story by the famous internet author, Xxharuki. A self-help book author Xu lives happily with his wife Jeana and their son. However, when a voluptuous and seductive tenant rents their apartment upstairs, Xus life is turned upside down.

programme.title: Bounty Hunters
programme.desc: A group of bounty hunters, including San, Yo, Cat, Swan and Bobo, are tasked to track down the culprit of a series of bombings that have plagued an international hotel group. Unfortunately, Swan, Cat and Bobo are kidnapped by the mastermind of the bombings. Can San and Yo save them? Will the bounty hunters accomplish their mission?

programme.title: The Eagle Shooting Heroes
programme.desc: Executive produced by Wong Kar Wai, The Eagle Shooting Heroes is loosely based on Louis Chas classics. Whilst mistaken identity and rampant gender confusion are on the menu, Sammo Hungs action direction and the incredible all-star casts also keep the laughs and thrills coming in this Hong Kong-style crazy comedy.

programme.title: The Way We Keep Dancing
programme.desc: This sequel of The Way We Dance features the plight of Hong Kongs grassroots performing artists as they fight against the governments plan to gentrify an industrial district where they settled in.

programme.title: Last Suspect
programme.desc: Lawyer Chen receives a mysterious call demanding her to defend a murder suspect after her daughter is kidnapped, and is told that she can only save her daughter by winning the case. As she starts investigation with the police and evidence emerges, Chen discovers the truth and reveals the mastermind. Can she rescue her daughter in time?

programme.title: Fallen Angels
programme.desc: The funkier cousin to Chungking Express, director Wong Kar Wai looks at five fallen angels who suffer love and loss amidst the crime and chaos of Hong Kongs neon nights in this movie. Karen Mok won Best Supporting Actress in the 15th Hong Kong Film Awards for her remarkable role as a broken-hearted party girl.

programme.title: The Captain
programme.desc: The movie is based on a real incident of Sichuan Airlines Flight 8633 on 14 May 2018. When the cockpit windshield shatters after takeoff, the Captain manages to land the airplane safely with his level-headed swift actions and sheer determination. This is lauded as a miracle in airline history.

programme.title: Wo Hu
programme.desc: The Hong Kong Police has placed more than a thousand undercover officers in various triad groups to bring down the largest criminal organization in Hong Kong. Betrayal, deceit and murder bring this group of "brothers" into a collision with the law and with each other!

programme.title: Golden Chicken
programme.desc: Ah Kam, a seasoned prostitute, gets locked inside an ATM vestibule with a thief. Both discover they are ill-fated in life and Ah Kam starts telling him her life story as a prostitute, from a teenage hooker to a PR girl in an upscale club in her thirties, as well as being a strip dancer, bar girl and masseuse.

programme.title: Tales from the Occult: Body and Soul
programme.desc: This horror anthology series returns to feature three spooky crime stories about an ex-hair model, a cat lover and the love triangle between a dental nurse, a dentist and a chef. The stories depict their paths from obsession to madness, eventually tipping them over to the dark side of human nature.

programme.title: Hail the Judge
programme.desc: A low level magistrate is run out of town for defending a beautiful murder suspect. Through a series of comedic events he ascends to the top rank & returns looking for revenge.

programme.title: A Witness out of the Blue
programme.desc: The police suspects that a jewel thief, found dead in his unit with all stolen goods missing, is killed by his gang leader. They also found the crime to be related to a jewel robbery many months ago, with the robbers involved being killed off one by one. In this complicated case, the polices only witness is a talking parrot from the crime scene.

programme.title: My Blue Summer
programme.desc: Zhi has been secretly in love with Nan since she met him once as a child. After graduating high school, Zhi realizes that she and Nan are in the same university, where they get to know each other by chance and become close friends. However, Zhi is still too shy to express her love for Nan. Will this long-term crush finally turn into true love?

programme.title: Flirting Scholar from the Future
programme.desc: Tiger, Lambert and Skinny Pig are massive fans of the movie, Flirting Scholar. One day, Skinny Pig who is an obscure inventor, puts together a movie time machine and accidentally sucks all of them into the movie of Flirting Scholar. The trio head off to Wah mansion to meet the maid Autumn can they find her and can they return to the present?

programme.title: Wu Xia
programme.desc: Martial artist Liu hides his identity and lives in a remote village with his wife Ah Yu and their two sons, but somehow gets embroiled in a bizarre murder case. Constable Xu is a kung fu fanatic, whose curiosity forces Liu into a death duel with the Sect Leader of the 72 Demons, and puts Lius family and homeland in a great danger...

programme.title: Far Far Away
programme.desc: A 28-year-old IT geek has only been in love once. Surprisingly, he ends up getting romantically involved with five different women this year and the one thing they have in common is that they all live in far flung areas of Hong Kong. After taking five intensive relationship courses within these 365 days, will he find the-one?

programme.title: L Storm
programme.desc: ICAC officer Luk and Chief Inspector Lau both hit a dead end when investigating their respective bribery and money laundering cases. When Luk is accused of bribery after being framed by the money launderers, he risks everything he has to find crucial evidence against them to clear his name.

programme.title: Vanguard
programme.desc: A businessman Qin Guo Li is being kidnapped in London and his daughter is also in danger. The international security team, Vanguard, is hired to rescue them. Tang Huan Ting, the founder, gathers an elite team to track them down across countries, from London to Africa and Dubai. In the process, they also discover another dangerous conspiracy.

programme.title: Fatal Visit
programme.desc: Yanny leaves Hong Kong for San Jose to visit her old friend Ling. Ling and her husband Tang seems to live an ideal and carefree life. However, during her five-day stay, Yanny uncovers the truth behind the faade as she reveals the unspeakable secrets that will propel all three down a fatal path of destruction.

programme.title: Cyber Heist
programme.desc: Hackers have caused a large-scale cyber attack, but luckily cyber security engineer Chun, manages to fend it off with his protective firewall system. To Chun's surprise, his boss is the mastermind of the attack, and when Chun gets trapped in a money laundering operation, he must fight against his boss in the cyber world to prove his innocence.

programme.title: Unleashed
programme.desc: Fok Kit is the hottest underground boxer with unbeatable records. To save their boxing studio from being sold, he must win the fight against Shaolin who is known as "Killing Machine". Fok Kit is defeated and badly hurt in the fight, which is a set-up by Lok, who wants to take revenge on Fok Kits master, Debo.

programme.title: Wu Kong
programme.desc: Set 500 years before the Monkey King Wu Kong wreaks havoc in the heavenly kingdom, the movie tells the story of how Wu Kong who, unwilling to bow to his own destiny, sets out to rebel against the gods.

programme.title: Lonely Eighteen
programme.desc: Set in the 1980s Hong Kong, Elaine and her best friend Ying enter the entertainment industry hoping to change their fates from poverty. Ying soon becomes a popular porn star but Elaine is lost between being her true self and an actress. When show business declines after a decade, their choices lead them to two different paths in life.

programme.title: The Macaque Monkey
programme.desc: The world is in chaos after the tree of life was burnt. Sun Wu Kong decides to return to the past to resurrect it, but his divine power is unstable after losing the golden hoop, and he must find his younger self to team up to find the power of time. As the six-eared Macaque Monkey also wants the power of time, they clash in a fierce battle

programme.title: Over My Dead Body
programme.desc: This dark comedy begins with an unidentified corpse appearing at the doorstep of a residential flat. Fearing that the corpse will turn their flats into "haunted flats", which will cause a drastic drop in the property value, the four families living on the same floor attempt to move the corpse away, embroiling themselves in chaos.

programme.title: The White Storm 3 Heaven or Hell
programme.desc: Hong Kong cop Billy works undercover in Suchat's drug cartel, while another undercover cop Wing successfully earns their trust in an incident and a brotherly bond is built among the three. When the police busts the syndicate, Suchat flees to the Golden Triangle with Billy and receives a tip-off about the betrayal within his circle of trust

programme.title: We are Family
programme.desc: Struggling as an extra, Chi Kwong joins a rent-a-family company run by Carlos and aspiring actress Catherine, and rent themselves out as make-believe relatives. As they surrogate different families, they unravel the complexities of family relationships, forging deeper connections along the way.

programme.title: MMA Diva
programme.desc: Xin Lan takes over her fathers MMA club which is heavily in debt due to poor business. After He Hua defeated Xin Lan, she replaces her to become the new top MMA Diva and challenges Xin Lans MMA club to a duel. As Xin Lan is injured, she seeks help from a retried MMA superstar to fight the battle on her behalf to reclaim the clubs and her honour.

programme.title: Endgame
programme.desc: A killer and a stage actor accidentally swapped their identities at a bathhouse. The actor must complete the killers mission while the killer thinks he is a hopeless actor after losing his memory during the accident. When the killer strives to become a successful stage actor, he also starts to recall what has happened

programme.title: Inner Senses
programme.desc: Haunted by recurring visions stemming from past traumas, Yan reaches out to psychiatrist Dr Jim to restore her sanity and overcome her troubled past. Yet, as Yan gradually heals, Jim finds himself haunted by the same disturbing images, as his suppressed memories resurface.

programme.title: Bodies at Rest
programme.desc: When three armed criminals barge into a morgue, a forensic doctor and his student must fight with their lives to stop the criminals from obtaining a bullet from inside a corpse that is a key piece of evidence in a deadly crime.

programme.title: The Jade Raksha
programme.desc: A fearsome swordswoman known as The Jade Raksha appears in the martial arts world and begins killing people whose surname is Yan. A swordsman figures out who she is and asks her why. Apparently a Yan killed her family 18 years ago and she only has vengeance on her mind

programme.title: Golden Swallow
programme.desc: A heroine finds herself in a love triangle with a swordsman and a warrior. They team up to conquer the evil forces of the martial arts world but she is unable to choose between both men even as they face a deadly duel.

programme.title: Song Of Orchid Island
programme.desc: Dr. He moves to the remote Lanyu island off the coast of Taiwan to look for his long lost father, and starts to run a clinic curing islanders who are bitten by the fatal red worms there. He meets Ya Lan who works as a nurse in his clinic and falls in love with him. Things get vicious for Dr. He as a jealous islander plots to get rid of him

programme.title: Heads For Sale
programme.desc: Hua is an upright and brave swordswoman who will stand up against villains and do anything for Luo, the man she loves. When Luo is sent to jail by the corrupted police, she sets out to free him and did not hesitate to chop off two bodyguards heads. In the process, she also stumbles across an old enemy of her father who is back seeking revenge.

programme.title: Scandal
programme.desc: The roguish scamp Zhen and his best friend Chia collects proof of corruption from the officials in this comedy-drama. After a string of blackmailing, they end up in positions of power, but what is to happen next?

programme.title: Legend Of The Fox
programme.desc: A young man, Chin, believes he is an orphan, until he meets three men and learns from them that his father was a great swordsman who was killed when he was trying to dispel rumors of a wrongdoing and return a lost sword to its rightful owner. Chin seeks out the mens help to take vengeance on the wrongful death of his father.

programme.title: Beyond the Great Wall
programme.desc: Wang Zhao Jun refuses to bribe the imperial painter, so he draws an ugly portrait of her, preventing her from being selected by the Emperor until they meet in person. The painter ends up in exile and plots for Wang to marry the Huns warlord as a revenge. The Emperor rejects this, provoking a war which is only averted when Wang sacrifices herself.

programme.title: Opium And The Kung-Fu Master
programme.desc: Tie Qiao San, head of the Ten Guangdong Tigers, is an honourable master with many disciples. As opium becomes popular among the nobles, Tie starts taking it and gradually harms his body. When an opium houses owner defeats Tie in a fight and he is only saved from being killed by his disciple, Tie vows to quit opium and get back on his feet.

programme.title: The Perfumed Arrow
programme.desc: A charming Huangmei Opera title, this is the story of Fei E, a Generals daughter who grows up fooling everyone that she is a boy, including her two closest schoolmates. When she has to choose one of them to marry, how will Fei E tell them that she is a girl? To complicate matters, a girl who Fei E saves one day only wants to be married to her!

programme.title: New Tales of the Flying Fox
programme.desc: In a great rendition of The Silver Fox and Legend of the Fox comes this exciting adventure, where the only thing between the clan leaders and certain death is Hui Ying-hung.

programme.title: The Blue and the Black Part 2
programme.desc: Continuing from the first movie, Tang Qi ends her career as a nightclub singer and starts searching battle-scarred China for her lover Chang, who is now entangled with Japanese invaders, communist insurgents, and a warlord's beautiful daughter.

programme.title: The Weird Man
programme.desc: During the Three Kingdoms period, a Taoist priest Yu Ji cures many patients with his supernatural powers and is loved by the people. However, the arrogant general Sun Che thinks that Yu Ji bewitches people and orders for him to be beheaded. Subsequently, the spirit of the Yu Ji rises from his dead body and takes revenge on Sun Che.

programme.title: Swift Sword
programme.desc: A righteous swordsman, Bai Yi Pang, seeks revenge on an evil clan but is crippled after being beaten up by them. Years later, a young man encounters Bai who is hiding in a cave. Bai decides to teach this determined young man his Swift Sword skills so that he can help Bai take revenge on the evil clan.

programme.title: The Crimson Palm
programme.desc: Poor student Lin is engaged to the daughter of a rich man who despises him because of his familys declining status. Lin visits his fiance before leaving for the Imperial examination, but finds a maid lying dead in blood. As Lins bloody handprint is left on the site, he is accused of the murder. How can Justice Bao prove his innocence?

programme.title: Raw Courage
programme.desc: After the Ming Emperor is overthrown and his infant son was put in the care of the Black Dragon Society, a traitorous martial arts clan attacks the society, forcing an inexperienced pair of swordsman and swordswoman to flee with the infant. Their journey to deliver the infant to safety is filled with dangers that would require help from other allies

programme.title: Sweet And Wild
programme.desc: Fang is a spunky young village girl who is not afraid to fight back against hooligans. She gets into trouble with the biggest hoodlum Tong when she foils his plans with a maid, causing Tong to plot a revenge. Luckily a man whom she is attracted to, Hai, comes in time to her rescue. Can they fight back?

programme.title: Little Dragon Maiden
programme.desc: With Hong Kong cinema's new wave, high flying, martial arts action of the 1980's, came a new wave of actors; teeny-bopper, canto-pop singer/stars with little or no martial arts background. However, when a film like LITTLE DRAGON MAIDEN intelligently mixes the old with the new, the results are pure golden magic. This costume-action, drama, love story features relative newcomer Leslie Cheung, who falls in love with the Dragon Maiden while learning the art of swordplay. The recipe is complete when veteran kung-fu stars Chen Kuan-tai and Lo Lieh add just enough weapon-wielding spice to make this film really cook. Cheung garnered international recognition in John Woo's A BETTER TOMORROW and Ronny Yu's THE BRIDE WITH WHITE HAIR.

programme.title: Call of the Sea
programme.desc: A young fisherman, Chin Hu is in love with his childhood friend Hsiao Yu. However, the only son of a town bully lusts after Hsiao Yus beauty and tries all possible ways to approach her. Chin Hu protects another woman from the bully one day, leading Hsiao Yu to misunderstand him and suspect that they are having an affair...

programme.title: The Wandering Swordsman
programme.desc: The wandering swordsman Yu Hsieh Erh has formidable sword skills and helps the poor by robbing from thieves and distributing the wealth. He meets a group of bandits who are planning to rob a convoy escorting some valuables and is tricked into participating in the robbery. Yu soon realizes his folly and returns to take revenge on the bandits.

programme.title: Madam White Snake
programme.desc: Linda Lin Dai is perfect as Pak Su-cheng, the stunning snake goddess who assumes a womanly form so that she can taste the pleasures of a human life! Pak seduces young scholar, Hsu Hsien when she recognises him as her saviour in another life 1,000 years ago. But when Buddhist monk Fa Hai finds out about the union, the pair is forced to split...

programme.title: Five Superfighters
programme.desc: A kung fu master and his three students lost everything after they are floored by a bully. To take revenge, the students find ways to learn from other kung fu masters and come back six months later to have a rematch with the bully on their masters birthday.

programme.title: Pale Passion
programme.desc: Fa is an obsessive man who loves his wife Ah Hsia but is easily jealous and abuses her. When she leaves him one day, Fa hooks up with another woman, Hsing. A deadly triangle develops when Fa runs into Ah Hsia again and decides to win her back

programme.title: Brothers Five
programme.desc: The five Kao brothers, separated since birth, are unaware that the master of Teng Lung Manor has killed their father. All five however, vow to defeat the vicious gangsters at the manor due to their bullying ways. After reuniting and with much discipline and hard work, the Kaos are prepared to face Lung and his gang.

programme.title: The Mirror and the Lichee
programme.desc: The curious title in this Huangmei Opera romance refers to the two props that signal a happy beginning between a scholar and a local beauty. The scholar polishes mirrors so as to be closer to his love, who signals her approval by tossing him some lichees. From that point on the course of their love becomes rocky, complete with murder and suicide.

programme.title: Diary of a Lady-killer
programme.desc: Tycoon Zhou is a playboy who is engaged to be married, but that did not keep him from working his charms on as many ladies as he can. He keeps a diary about his romantic escapades and soon, the women with whom he has been intimate with are being murdered one by one. Zhou becomes the number one suspect by the police but is the killer someone else?

programme.title: Princess Iron Fan
programme.desc: As Monkey and his gang make their way to the West through Fire Mountain, they ran into the evil Princess Iron Fan, Madam White Bone and her sexy sister, and have to fight their way through.

programme.title: Return to the 36th Chamber
programme.desc: The second film of the trilogy, Gordon Liu plays Zhou Ren Jie, a man who impersonates a monk in order to learn kung fu in Shaolin, and eventually creates his own Shaolin style of scaffolding kung fu.

programme.title: The Dancing Millionairess
programme.desc: Peter was a key dancer in a dance troupe and applied to be the chauffeur of a rich girl, Betty. When he is rumoured to be her lover, Betty is furious and goes undercover as a reporter to investigate the rumour. They fall in love in the process, and after putting Peter through many tests, they finally seal their love with a dance.

programme.title: The Treasure Hunters
programme.desc: Fans of the international star Alexander Fu Sheng were aghast. Their idol had broken both his legs and was recuperating. Everyone wondered: would he be able to return to the action comedies for which he was so famous? This movie was the answer, and it left no doubt that he had made a full recovery. Liu Chia-yung, brother of preeminent martial arts moviemaker Liu Chia-liang, was famous in his own right for kung-fu comedies, and he out-did himself with this one. Imagine Bob Hope and Bing Crosby with the skills of Jet Li and Jackie Chan, and youve got an idea of the fun and fury inherent in this delightful tale of two con men vying for a horde of hidden gold. Add to the mix a Shaolin monk (played by "Master Killer" Gordon Liu Chia-hui), a powerfully brutal villain, and his equally dangerous mute sister (future director Yang Tsing-tsing), and youve got one of the most internationally loved kung-fu capers ever made.

programme.title: Moonlight Serenade
programme.desc: A sweet inn-keepers daughter is witness to a perverted rape, leading to more danger than most romantic dramas can handle. Can her true love rescue her in time? For this movie, the moonlight serenade is the sound of suspense, leading to more danger than most romantic dramas can handle.

programme.title: The Flag of Iron
programme.desc: When super director Chang Cheh found new talent and blood with "The Five Venoms" actors, most of which were trained in the highly acrobatic Chinese opera and well versed with exotic martial arts weapons, this created a new spark for his use of bizarre weapons in his films. The Flag Of Iron is one of 20 movies that he directed featuring the utterly flabbergasting and physically exhausting action bits created by these five dudes. You have the good guys from the righteous clan versus the bad guys from the villainous clan and it's so filled with "don't-blink-or-you-will-miss-something" gags, you will need to watch it over and over again so you can see the things you missed.

programme.title: Hong Kong Rhapsody
programme.desc: Hong Kong rhapsody is a musical extravaganza full of song and dance! Peter Chen-Ho stars as a playboy magician who changes his ways after he becomes the guardian of a young singer (Li Ching), the daughter of a deceased magician friend.

programme.title: The Thunderbolt Fist
programme.desc: A vicious Japanese judo expert wants to prove that Chinese are the sick people of Asia and sets out to sabotage and kill the best martial artists in dangerous tournaments. To save his son from this, the head of Ping Pai Boxing Institute sends him to the mountains to learn the powerful Thunderbolt Fist technique from master fighter, Red Butterfly.

programme.desc: Guitar-playing rich kid, Yang Fan, heads to Japan to join a rock 'n' roll band where he soon finds himself competing for the affections of two beautiful girls.

Hero is a word we often hear in the world of sports, but heroism is not always about achievements on the field of play. 42 tells the story of two men -- the great Jackie Robinson (Chadwick Boseman) and the legendary Brooklyn Dodgers manager Branch Rickey (Harrison Ford) -- whose brave stand against prejudice forever changed the world by changing the game of baseball. In 1946, Rickey signed Robinson to the team, breaking Major League Baseball's infamous color line. Facing racism from every side, Robinson demonstrated tremendous courage by letting his talent on the field do the talking -- ultimately winning over fans and his teammates, and paving the way for others to follow.

programme.desc: When their father passes away, four grown siblings (Jason Bateman, Tina Fey, Adam Driver, Corey Stoll), bruised and banged up by their respective adult lives, are forced to return to their childhood home and live under the same roof together for a week, along with their over-sharing mother (Jane Fonda) and an assortment of spouses, exes and might-have-beens. Confronting their history and the frayed states of their relationships among the people who know and love them best, they ultimately reconnect in hysterical and emotionally affecting ways amid the chaos, humor, heartache and redemption that only families can provide-- driving us insane even as they remind us of our truest, and often best, selves. programme.title: Guardians of the Wild 2 - Big Move Ep1
programme.desc: The Lilayi Elephant Nursery near Lusaka in Zambia is home to four orphan elephants. The two oldest, four-year- olds Musolole and Zambezi, have been here since they were just a few months old. These boisterous babies are out-growing the nursery and its time to move to big school. Two hundred miles away, in the heart of Kafue National Park, lies elephant heaven - Camp Phoenix, the projects release facility, where older orphans are already adapting to life in the wild.

programme.title: Guardians of the Wild 2 - Zambia's Peaceful Primates Ep2
programme.desc: Kasanka National Park in Zambia is home to an unusual species of baboon. Kinda baboons have turned their backs on the aggressive displays of dominance usually associated with these large monkeys and lead altogether more peaceful lives. Living alongside one troop is a dedicated team of researchers whose mission it is to uncover these baboons secrets and understand what makes them who they are.

programme.title: Shark Squad 1 - Chasing Mako Ep3
programme.desc: In some of the most-remote regions on the planet, researchers dive deep and brave danger to unlock secret shark behaviours, challenge myths about sharks, and fight for the protection of these supreme predators before its too late.

programme.title: Uptown Otters 1 - A Busy Bay Ep3
programme.desc: Get ready to rumble in Marina Bay, where the Nomads and Townies are squatting while Anna and the Bay Family are away upriver. Soak up the peaceful otter life in this luxurious waterway before the surprise early return of its rightful owners.

programme.desc: Join Julz and park scout Simon Chulu as they track the Kakuli pack, who they filmed last year, and a Manzi faction whove ditched a tracking collar and broken away from the group. Spot the Kakumbi making a kill before a happy Manzi reunion ensues.

programme.title: Great Parks of Africa 2 - The Garden Route Ep1
programme.desc: In a park where land meets sea, the natural elements combine to create wonderful variety. Cola-colored water feeds forests green and dense. Fire and wind fuel growth in great diversity and rock shapes a coastline of many faces. Life thrives here - from the magnificent to the bizarre. This is the Garden Route National Park.

programme.title: Great Parks of Africa 2 - Kruger's Pafuri Ep2
programme.desc: In the northern reaches of the Kruger National Park, life depends on one thing water. In a land burdened by heat and drought a single ribbon cuts its reliable course through the wilderness. Its a lifeline to all creatures, great and small.

programme.title: Great Parks of Africa 2 - Augrabies Falls Ep3
programme.desc: Augrabies is where the mighty Orange River plunges over the awesome 56 meter Augrabies waterfall. Derived from a word oukurubes which means place of thunder in the indigenous language of the Nama-Khoi this land is the heart of a harsh and sun-beaten world with flashes of brilliant color and a thunderous roar.

programme.title: Great Parks of Africa 2 - The Lower Zambezi Ep4
programme.desc: Food, water and shelter are essential to all life on earth from the smallest of beings to the largest, and along the banks of one of Africas greatest rivers, some animals struggle while others thrive. A rhythm drives all animals as they journey in search of what they need to survive, and each must decide where and when to move if theyre to succeed... These are the magical worlds of the Lower Zambezi.

programme.title: Great Parks of Africa 2 - Hluhluwe-Imfolozi Ep5
programme.desc: In the heart of Zululand, South Africa, lies the oldest game reserve on the African continent Hluhluwe-iMfolozi. Here, Southern white rhinos have found protection from people in times of turmoil. Hunted almost to extinction at the end of the 19th century, the parks establishment gave rhinos a lifeline breeding them back from extinction.

programme.title: Secret Life of the Koala 1 - Koala Country Ep1
programme.desc: Despite being one of Australias best-known marsupials, koalas live only in the east and southeast parts of the continent. Learn how their lives and behaviors vary in these different regions.

programme.title: Secret Life of the Koala 1 - Breeding Season Ep2
programme.desc: Koalas may seem solitary and inert, but mating season brings a dramatic shift in their behavior, leading to movement, contact, and conflict. As breeding season begins, follow two large males on a mission to mate.

programme.title: New Kids in the Wild 2 - Rio the Giant River Otter Pup Ep5
programme.desc: Visit the last stronghold of the giant river otter in Brazils beautiful Pantanal wetland. Track pup Rio and his siblings as they test the waters, team up to evade a jaguar ambush, and become a cohesive family unit that hunts and thrives together.

programme.title: Undiscovered Vistas 3 - Lost World of the Yucatan Ep1
programme.desc: Dive under Mexicos Yucatn rainforest into an elaborate network of flooded caves called cenotes. Learn how underground rivers feed the waterless surface on their way to the sea, supporting legions of bats, howler monkeys, and more curious species.

programme.title: Undiscovered Vistas 3 - Wild Heart of Sierra Gorda Ep2
programme.desc: Find surprises in Mexicos untamed Sierra Gorda biosphere. Prowl the arid semi-desert with horned lizards, marvel at axolotl regeneration in the river-fed foothills, and soar with monarch butterflies in the treetops high above a hazy cloud forest.

programme.title: Undiscovered Vistas 3 - Costa Rica: Sky to Sea Ep3
programme.desc: Visit the Monteverde cloud forest, where swirling mists feed Costa Ricas mighty rivers and create a haven for biodiversity. See some of its 750 tree species, hang out with sloths and monkeys, and watch nature heal after decades of deforestation.

programme.desc: Race to contain a case of malaria brought in by orphaned infant Cesia, then assess surrogate mum Sris plan to help Bumi. See the positive influence of Daput, a wild orangutan mum, on the college females before a shocking thief raids the food store.

programme.desc: Hunt for missing nursery-class orphan Lahei and see shy Rumba try her weak left hand in a nest-building session. Watch younger Delilah school Bumi in class, then find out if Beni and Valentino will make the grade and finally earn their freedom.

programme.title: Orangutan Jungle School 3 - Graduation Day Ep6
programme.desc: Congratulate the new Orangutan Jungle School graduates, who arent all spring chickens. Follow the convoy to the release site, where the team bids their friends a poignant farewell, then enjoy raucous celebrations as Molly and Bumi move up a grade.

programme.desc: Chase the team as they triage patients from a hoarding case, then free a tangled-up ibis with rescue officers Jo and Chantelle. Check on a baby koala that took a swan dive with vet Mel and play the waiting game with a deadly eastern brown snake.

programme.title: Wildlife ER 2 - Duckling Dramas Ep5
programme.desc: Deal with duelling duckling roundups and find out if vet Karina calls in specialists to treat koala Spikes leg fracture. Get to the bottom of stomach issues plaguing baby echidnas Ping and Pong, and meet koala Jarrah, who seems to have lost his way.

programme.title: Wildlife ER 2 - Into the Sunset Ep6
programme.desc: Contend with a flood of abandoned koala joeys, then join vet nurse Nick on a hunt for natural remedies to treat a wallabys gut ailment. Ponder options for a baby bat stuck in a tree and look on as vet Karina operates on a barn owls fractured wing.

programme.desc: Encounter an elephant as Julz and Henry from the ZCP track the Kakumbi pups, who face off with a stubborn, razor-tusked warthog. Follow Thandie Mweetwa, ZCPs lion specialist, who counts the prides that are pushing the Manzi out of their territory.

programme.title: Rooted 1 - Memoirs of Acacia Ep1
programme.desc: Across rippled dunes, in the wind-swept grasslands of the southern Kalahari towers a magnificent Camelthorn. It has stood here for two centuries. This tree is never lonely, learn how it provides food, shelter and a hunting ground to many creatures.

programme.title: Rooted 1 - Sweet Seduction Ep2
programme.desc: Discover the story of the much loved Sausage Tree, whose nectar filled blooms and sausage shaped fruits entice animals of all kinds, from insects to elephants. See how the very animals who rely on this generous tree ensure its proliferation.

programme.title: Rooted 1 - The Giant Ep3
programme.desc: In a misty South African forest grows a six hundred year old Outeniqua Yellowwood. At forty meters tall, she towers above the canopy and is one of the few remaining of her kind. Follow her captivating story, unique as the ecosystem in her branches.

programme.title: Rooted 1 - Rock Splitter Ep4
programme.desc: The Namaqua Rock Fig Tree stands rooted on the slope of a rocky hill in Namaqualand, South Africa. It is the ultimate survivor, able to withstand the unforgiving conditions in a landscape facing ever rising temperatures and less and less rainfall each year.

programme.title: Rooted 1 - The Hollow Heart Ep5
programme.desc: This is the incredible story of a tree that has been around for eight hundred years that can withstand the harshest conditions and that is more loved by insects, birds and animals than any otherthe enormous Baobab. Rooted on the savannah of Malilangwe Game Reserve in southern Zimbabwe.

programme.title: Secret Life of the Wombat 1 - Wombat Wood Ep1
programme.desc: In the cool highlands near Australias Snowy Mountains is Wombat Wood. There, dotted amongst the trees and dense foliage, are over a hundred wombat burrows. But when some of the burrows are flooded, the wombats need to find safety.

programme.title: Secret Life of the Wombat 1 - Joey's Journey Ep2
programme.desc: Wombats are solitary, slow-moving creatures, but breeding time brings out their energy, aggression and lots of play. Meet a southern hairy-nosed wombat named Birri, whos trying to find a mate, along with a female named Winnie and her joey, Fred.

programme.title: Surviving the Amazon 1 - A Life Among Trees Ep3
programme.desc: How many trees can you find in the Amazon? And whats it like to live up in them? Travel through the canopy and see how more than 1200 species of trees coexist. Plus, follow monkeys and other creatures who call these trees home.

programme.title: Surviving the Amazon 1 - Dry Season Ep4
programme.desc: The dry season is the toughest time of year. With lower water levels and less space, animals need to quickly learn new skills to surviveand if they dont, predatory vultures will swoop in for a feast.

programme.title: Surviving the Amazon 1 - Jungle Juniors Ep5
programme.desc: Every year, more than 200,000 monkeys in Peru are trafficked illegally. Almost all are babies. Watch as these little ones learn to survive without their moms and try to make new friends along the way.

programme.title: Wild Latin America 1 - Humpback Birth of a Giant Ep1
programme.desc: Follow the first months of a newborn humpback whales life in the waters off the Pacific Coast of Columbia. See how his mother nurtures him through sickness, supports his body, protects him under attack, and prepares him for an epic journey.

programme.title: Wild Latin America 1 - Squirrel Monkey Island Ep2
programme.desc: Travel deep into the Columbian rainforest, where its mating season for one of the most clever monkey species in the world. Witness the most important time of year for male squirrel monkeys that have been bulking up to impress females for months.

programme.title: Kingdom of the Tide
programme.desc: Low tide exposes a band of shore called the intertidal zone. Its a place of stunning extremes, attacked by hurricane force waves and exposed to baking heat. Creatures here have evolved in countless bizarre ways. Scientists explore this alien realm.

programme.title: Super Shark Highway 1 - Food, Glorious Food Ep1
programme.desc: Embark on a dangerous tagging mission in South Australia that will show what sharks eat and why they gather in feeding hot spots. Then head north as a team chases tiger, bull, and hammerhead sharks and outfits one with a 360-degree dorsal camera.

programme.title: Super Shark Highway 1 - Love Bites Ep2
programme.desc: Track a pregnant shark along the Great Barrier Reef and see if she leads a team of scientists to her hidden pupping ground. Then search for signs of mating along the southern coast that could reveal a very shy female megashark in search of a partner.

programme.title: Shark Squad 1 - How Smart Are Sharks? Ep4
programme.desc: Often portrayed as mindless eating machines prone to attacking humans, sharks are more complex and intelligent than previously thought. Find out how these graceful top predators interact, choose friends, and even teach other sharks.

programme.title: Great Blue Wild 3 - Save the Giants Ep2
programme.desc: The wild coastline of Mozambique stretches along more than 1,600 miles - an area teeming with a diversity of marine life. Some of the worlds largest filter feeders are attracted to this nutrient-rich water. But even these large creatures are defenceless against reckless overfishing. Two of Mozambiques leading marine researchers, Andrea Marshall and Nakia Cullain, set out to find one of the oceans most secretive animals and protect its most well known, before its too late.

programme.title: Great Blue Wild 3 - Macro Mozambique Ep3
programme.desc: The coast of Mozambique is home to giants, like humpbacks and whale sharks, but the tiniest species play just as big of a role in the ecosystem. Meet the scientists who are working against the clock to protect coastal creatures big and small.

programme.title: Kingdom of the Tide
programme.desc: Low tide exposes a band of shore called the intertidal zone. Its a place of stunning extremes, attacked by hurricane force waves and exposed to baking heat. Creatures here have evolved in countless bizarre ways. Scientists explore this alien realm.

programme.title: Sort Your Life Out S3 Ep4
programme.desc: Stacey and her crack team help single mum Claire and her five boys transform their home.

programme.title: George Clarke's Remarkable Renovations S3 Ep7
programme.desc: Pie Factory, Lancashire - George Clarke meets Sam and Jimmy who are converting a 5,000 square foot old pie factory into an incredible new home.

programme.title: Junior Bake Off S8 Ep11
programme.desc: It's Finals Week and our junior bakers dive into Chocolate Day, as they combine chocolate and miso in a sweet-and-salty bake and create mini chocolate mousse mirror glaze cakes.
